<body>
  <h1>Chocolate Cake</h1>

  <!-- Using the external image URL you provided -->
  <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/3b/ea/ae/3beaae5b7d22035c2b2edf84eeaa6c2f.jpg"
       alt="A slice of chocolate cake with frosting">

  <h2>Description</h2>
  <p>This chocolate cake is rich, moist, and perfect for any celebration. Easy to make and topped with creamy chocolate frosting.</p>

  <h2>Ingredients</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>2 cups all-purpose flour</li>
    <li>2 cups sugar</li>
    <li>3/4 cup cocoa powder</li>
    <li>2 tsp baking powder</li>
    <li>1/2 tsp salt</li>
    <li>1 cup milk</li>
    <li>1/2 cup vegetable oil</li>
    <li>2 eggs</li>
    <li>1 tsp vanilla extract</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Steps</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C) and grease a cake pan.</li>
    <li>Mix dry ingredients in a large bowl.</li>
    <li>Add milk, oil, eggs, and vanilla, then mix until smooth.</li>
    <li>Pour batter into prepared pan and bake for 30–35 minutes.</li>
    <li>Let the cake cool before frosting and serving.</li>
  </ol>
